title: Big Train Series 1 (1998).DVDRip-scOOpy
description:
Excellent British sketch comedy show from the nineties. The absolute best thing about this is the staring contest. Comedic genius.

This is a rip of the ISO that is floating around here. This is much smaller, and you can download the episodes individually if you like, and watch them without waiting for the full 8gb ISO to download.

But I'm sure you guys already know the advantages of individual AVIs over a full ISO.

Thanks to the original guys for seeding the ISO, I hope more people will seed this and will have a chance to see this brilliant stuff now that it is in AVI format.
